            "value": {
              "exitCode": 0,
              "signal": "",
              "stdout": "{\"body\":\"<!-- li-agent -->\\n## Agent deliverable\\n- [x] Branch pushed and PR opened (not draft)\\n- [x] CI triggered on PR\\n- [x] Tests added / updated — paths: `benchmarks/tier2_physics/md_lennard_jones/li/main.li`, scoped tier-2 peers, `benchmarks/harness/bench.py`\\n- [x] Bench evidence — `./scripts/sim-plan-gates.sh` (scoped `bench-package.sh --timing`, `sim-bench-memory.sh`)\\n- [x] Release notes / CHANGELOG if required by repo policy — `docs/reports/sim-plan/algos/md_lennard_jones.md`\\n- [ ] merge-approved (human adds after review)\\n\\n## Summary\\n\\nCloses **sim-p0-md-lj-li-parity**: tier-2 `md_lennard_jones` Li driver now emits the same energy-drift checksum as native (`0.6892536936825765`) via `li_md_kernel()` + `li_rt_volatile_sink_f64(li_md_checksum())`. Removed `li_pure=True` on the bench spec so `LI_EXTRA_C` links `md_core.c`. Applied the same sink pattern to other `li-sim-scientific` tier-2 smokes so package-scoped gates pass.\\n\\n## Test plan\\n\\n- [x] `export CC=clang-22 && python3 benchmarks/harness/bench.py --verify-results --tier 2 --only md_lennard_jones`\\n- [x] `./scripts/sim-plan-gates.sh`\\n\\nMade with [Cursor](https://cursor.com)\",\"commits\":[{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-21T20:54:17Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-21T20:54:17Z\",\"messageBody\":\"- Fix routes_overlap in httpd_config.py (exact vs prefix)\\n- Add validate-httpd-config.py, flatten-httpd-config.py, lic CLI alias\\n- Runtime Bearer 401 gate + auth flatten keys in li_rt_net.c\\n- check-httpd-overlap-reject.py; fix run_httpd_config.sh rc capture\\n- packages/li-net-httpd/examples/auth_bearer.toml\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): M1 overlap reject, validate/flatten, Bearer auth\",\"oid\":\"4ec6abc701d191e579fcc4d6faa6cf6269ae4080\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-21T21:38:04Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-21T21:38:04Z\",\"messageBody\":\"- scripts/httpd-plan-loop.py drives plan todos via Cursor SDK httpd_implementer\\n- httpd-m1-baseline.md records merged work and stale PR policy\\n- li_rt_str_prefix_is_get / parse_request_len_tag fixes borrowck on parse_request\\n- HTTPD_SKIP_LI_ROUTING_BIN for compile-only routing gate until ABI fix\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): autonomous plan loop + E0311 parse_request fix\",\"oid\":\"d820fc0d37526cec594617901a197bbf4136c733\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-21T22:36:50Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-21T22:36:50Z\",\"messageBody\":\"- run_httpd_config: --allow-open-vc + HTTPD_SKIP_LI_ROUTING_BIN\\n- CHANGELOG union; release notes\",\"messageHeadline\":\"merge(httpd): rebase plan-loop on main (#163/#164)\",\"oid\":\"20b92cd1a6620a716ec4bc410c8045c18ac7ab38\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T08:31:29Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T08:31:39Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(httpd): plan loop disk store + flatten without route rate fields\",\"oid\":\"62e222b6166abaa0364ad7f770fa28aa3ecc44f5\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T08:43:40Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T08:43:40Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(httpd): reload-cursor-env probe; unset dashboard URL in CURSOR_SDK\",\"oid\":\"9d0e2ae3123676d3f06ec22eb918aadea714c95c\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T08:45:53Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T08:45:53Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(httpd): gates use lic --allow-open-vc after strict-by-default merge\",\"oid\":\"9d30de66509b486e12a3b701ccca684d6d6c700c\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T10:12:38Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"julian.kleber@sail.black\",\"id\":\"U_kgDODFke_A\",\"login\":\"cap-jmk-real\",\"name\":\"Julian M. Kleber\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T10:12:38Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Add non-Linux epoll_ctl_add_listen_i stub so li-httpd links on Darwin,\\nwire build-li-httpd.sh into plan gates and CI, and mark plan todo completed\\nafter test-auth-bearer.sh passes on real runtime config.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(httpd): complete m1-bearer-auth gate on build/li-httpd\",\"oid\":\"261e899162b24192442969feb2e507b1176f1b68\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T10:56:05Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"julian.kleber@sail.black\",\"id\":\"U_kgDODFke_A\",\"login\":\"cap-jmk-real\",\"name\":\"Julian M. Kleber\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T10:56:05Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Add routing table cases (method_reject, host_suffix), config_reject\\noverlap fixture, run_routing.sh harness, and green Li match_route oracles\\nin httpd-plan-gates. Mark plan todo m1-routing-tests completed.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): complete m1-routing-tests table cases and overlap reject\",\"oid\":\"17369f591e93eddb65f9eb7fa4437ac2b755fda2\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T11:04:14Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"julian.kleber@sail.black\",\"id\":\"U_kgDODFke_A\",\"login\":\"cap-jmk-real\",\"name\":\"Julian M. Kleber\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T11:04:14Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Add config_desugar fixtures for prefix_strip and header extras, loop\\ngolden checks in run_httpd_config.sh, and align C loader/explain with\\nPython httpd_config.py for route-key extras.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): complete m1-toml-desugar goldens and C route extras\",\"oid\":\"0b57c41e2c3c66c255093b492965e6cd292b9dd2\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T11:04:39Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"julian.kleber@sail.black\",\"id\":\"U_kgDODFke_A\",\"login\":\"cap-jmk-real\",\"name\":\"Julian M. Kleber\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T11:04:39Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"chore(lic): code_implementer post-hook commit\",\"oid\":\"babdad01570e5023ea3685777a34540b231991fc\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T13:27:32Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCc8rkw\",\"login\":\"S4il0r\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T13:27:32Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Require limits.rate_limit_rps when routes use proxy: (Python + desugar),\\nadd reject fixture and agent_gateway_limits example. Merge goal-directed\\nhttpd-plan-loop (code_implementer, --goal-file); prefer M1 todos over w0\\nblockers. Gates support HTTPD_GATES_SKIP_LIC_BUILD for Python-only CI.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): M1 proxy rate-limit validation and goal-directed plan loop\",\"oid\":\"812e76783c6b92599eedeae9506de990bef7073c\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T13:31:34Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCc8rkw\",\"login\":\"S4il0r\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T13:31:34Z\",\"messageBody\":\"… lic\\n\\nReject x-upstream-*, x-route-*, and hop-by-hop names in route-key extras;\\ndocument allowlist per httpd plan. Skip build-li-httpd bearer test when\\nHTTPD_GATES_SKIP_LIC_BUILD=1 so Python-only plan gates pass.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): M1 ingress header allowlist and skip bearer gate without…\",\"oid\":\"291865b859bc09a5c9d1949b73754c2e5c2fee05\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T13:42:40Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCc8rkw\",\"login\":\"S4il0r\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T13:42:40Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Add Debian 12 setup script (apt LLVM 18, user Node, env.d) and a short\\nagent/developer tutorial for engine: toolchain, httpd loop, env, troubleshooting.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"docs: devbox Li development guide and setup-li-devbox.sh\",\"oid\":\"6171965a3acee6452da2f76620e79b650c857ceb\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T13:51:07Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-code-implementer\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T13:51:12Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Wire proxy rate_limit_rps policy into lic httpd validate-config (C loader),\\nadd lb_mode_from_name Li wrapper + smoke test, and mark m1-core plan todo done.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): complete m1-core rate-limit validate-config and LB smoke\",\"oid\":\"4615bef311582077ae7931e516ef8d3d8c3f3f07\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T13:57:00Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOCc8rkw\",\"login\":\"S4il0r\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T13:57:29Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Default LI_DEVBOX_NODE_VERSION to 24.16.0 in setup-li-devbox.sh and docs.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"chore(devbox): standardize on Node 24.16 LTS\",\"oid\":\"93166c9236eb66255c2a562119285cad480cbbb7\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T14:07:28Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T14:07:53Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Set LI_REPO_WORKFLOW_* for the httpd PR branch, recover unpushed work\\nfrom lic checkout and workspace clones after each agent iteration, and\\nrequire agents to push before finishing.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"httpd plan loop: push recovery and PR branch tracking\",\"oid\":\"95803583524811b9b3e7fa6fbc1ccc9807985612\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:23:55Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"bot@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjU4MjEwNjIy\",\"login\":\"bot\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-bot\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:23:55Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Resolve conflicts: main wins httpd-plan-loop.py; keep M1 routing/auth\\nfrom httpd branch; fold LLVM 22 + li-tests manifest gates from main.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"merge(main): integrate #172 plan-loop fixes and #174 ecosystem CI\",\"oid\":\"e807a69147b0f48dfbaa94315a76f813ca8ce941\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:25:53Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"bot@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjU4MjEwNjIy\",\"login\":\"bot\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-bot\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:26:00Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"docs(ecosystem): PR hygiene record after #172/#174 merge\",\"oid\":\"8dc61a311362a03977fdc5abace2c732cd12b5cd\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:36:28Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"bot@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjU4MjEwNjIy\",\"login\":\"bot\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-bot\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:36:28Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Ubuntu 24.04 apt has no clang-22 package; match main CI job install path.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(ci): use ci-install-llvm.sh in all GHA workflows\",\"oid\":\"3ee05989ff2f370b9243e4b9f5f65f6d2001b11a\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:36:42Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"bot@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjU4MjEwNjIy\",\"login\":\"bot\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-bot\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:36:42Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"docs(ecosystem): org-wide PR hygiene record 2026-05-22\",\"oid\":\"49c75a745367860251a6b86d95f1d2dfb78dbfbe\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:49:13Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"bot@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"MDQ6VXNlcjU4MjEwNjIy\",\"login\":\"bot\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-bot\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:49:40Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Remove duplicate extern from li-http (already in std.runtime.seam);\\nimport seam so lb_mode_from_name and httpd smokes compile together.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(http): use seam extern for httpd_lb_mode_from_arg_i\",\"oid\":\"d0338fe19b933d5a22d3b35929c0ebc6c4ea58f6\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:59:01Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@li-langverse.local\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T15:59:01Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Add run-local-pages-benchmarks skill for Actions-free site refresh.\",\"oid\":\"505fedec6a4a97f8035095f3c0a4f89e636fa636\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:06:23Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@li-langverse.local\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:06:23Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Publish ubuntu24+LLVM22 via GITHUB_TOKEN-only workflow; prepare-docker-ci-image\\npulls public ghcr.io/li-langverse/lic-ci or builds locally without secrets.\\nAlign C validate-config ingress allowlist with Python; skip auth-bearer smoke\\nwhen li-httpd build fails.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Add GHCR prebuilt CI Docker image and wire local-ci --docker.\",\"oid\":\"b7ff4fab561f4ec411f0ff17e0bb8f822a3fe019\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:07:22Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@li-langverse.local\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:07:22Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Agents must run compile/CI in the foreground with explicit exit=$? per step;\\nforbid redirect-to-log and tail-only pipelines that mask failures.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Add always-on rule for visible shell output during builds and tests.\",\"oid\":\"88bff6930ff8686b4e606dfa21f1f389b2aee3e1\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:07:56Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@li-langverse.local\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:07:56Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Docs: clarify macOS/Windows cannot run as Docker CI on Linux.\",\"oid\":\"53899aeb24bc9110057f3d6076871f72942ae5f8\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:14:47Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@li-langverse.local\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:14:47Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Add lsb-release and software-properties-common for llvm.sh; auto-detect\\npodman when docker socket is denied; skip auth-bearer TCP smoke in containers.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Fix Ubuntu CI image build and run local-ci via podman.\",\"oid\":\"6e470f6a7cd457cc99fe386938c74dd8256d6e36\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:15:45Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@li-langverse.local\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:15:45Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Shared resolve_container_runtime in scripts/lib/container-runtime.sh.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Prefer podman over docker for local CI containers when both exist.\",\"oid\":\"5e4c19e701a80cd83c01db1930d49c9070c42e2d\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:16:56Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@li-langverse.local\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:16:56Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Keep ubuntu24-llvm22 as optional GHA parity tag; podman still preferred\\nover docker when both are available.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Default CI container image to Debian 12 (bookworm + LLVM 22).\",\"oid\":\"601b68e1781149b6b9dc6a0e0325aac8fe95c78a\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:20:46Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@li-langverse.local\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:20:46Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Clarify that containers build lic from mounted source; add master plan\\ngate for future GHCR tags with pinned compiler binaries.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Docs: CI images are toolchain-only; defer release images with baked lic.\",\"oid\":\"8a922f8c316a34d05add788d0ceed468df2bc8d7\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:25:28Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@li-langverse.local\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:25:28Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Remove ecosystem step from GHA benchmarks workflow; ci-bench no longer runs bench_ecosystem by default.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Align lic harness tiers: tier 3 is HTTP, tier 5 is deferred ecosystem.\",\"oid\":\"f091480d5fbc1d19ed39b08612a5a8e566c8c765\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:46:40Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@li-langverse.local\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-langverse-agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T16:46:40Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Demo package keeps its own mirror CI; lic ci.sh should not fail on li-demo smoke.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"ci: skip li-demo in workspace build — not a lic compiler gate.\",\"oid\":\"e8e3d3654726d5fb8131c905a2c06c6e21542166\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T17:01:02Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T17:01:02Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Track PR branch via LI_REPO_WORKFLOW_*; recover unpushed clones after each\\nagent run; refresh benchmarks + development overview via refresh-live-sites.\\nAdd httpd-plan-overnight.sh for bounded batch runs.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"httpd overnight loop: push recovery, local Pages refresh\",\"oid\":\"f0e7d02648600975530dd9230fb58c93ccb52a82\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T17:01:37Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T17:01:37Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"httpd gates: restore HTTPD_GATES_SKIP_LIC_BUILD for plan loop\",\"oid\":\"96a0334828fff636962ee8c231b73dafab768f2a\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T17:10:12Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T17:10:12Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"httpd overnight: default 30 iterations\",\"oid\":\"82de5f62ce7bc8c7f8b78fc1a90708f2d99d4c24\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T17:23:28Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T17:23:28Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…OTel\\n\\nImplements plan todo m15-agent: validate stream_idle/max/concurrent_streams,\\n[[route.match]] x-model pools, req