83a8142dc737625519f60c042d7df5a451\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T18:40:41Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:31:21Z\",\"messageBody\":\"After the initial --max batch, httpd-plan-until-deadline.sh keeps starting\\nnew plan-loop batches until the local deadline (default 08:00).\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"httpd overnight: continue batches until 08:00 local\",\"oid\":\"c1957ae94bc10737556e071516fd011f77fda9d2\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T18:43:51Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:31:21Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Matmul kernels match C init and reduction; simd_dot uses the shared dot_core\\nuntil pure-Li survives -ffast-math without being folded to zero.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Align tier-1 Li benchmarks with native checksum verification.\",\"oid\":\"6fff6245856c75778263258627783b3e97b429ca\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:17:21Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:31:21Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Tier-1 verify checks float64 kernel specs (large + exact small-N), result\\nmagnitude floors, and Li wall-time floors on pure-Li rows to catch DCE.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Add normative benchmark references independent of other runtimes.\",\"oid\":\"763709d62f4f66229617e9a587cd937ad21d3cb8\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:18:02Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:31:21Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Documents normative reference.py checks, scaled goldens, and cross-lang\\nsanity checks in li-benchmark-correctness.mdc.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Add Cursor rule for benchmark correctness-over-parity philosophy.\",\"oid\":\"4ecce1ebac095e400af90b6f53cfe36f057881cd\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:31:16Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:31:21Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Co-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Add run-goal-directed-plan-loop skill; gitignore plan-loop artifacts\",\"oid\":\"b20845a6724187d908f92e5e44b5c3c305a3b62d\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:31:59Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:32:03Z\",\"messageBody\":\"data/httpd-plan-loop/ was gitignored after agent runs had already committed\\n~60k lines of iter/overnight logs. Remove from index; keep state.json.example.\\nAlso ignore data/local-ci*.log.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Stop tracking plan-loop logs and local-ci artifacts\",\"oid\":\"929a2335fa17d2ed0139c6f4bf8251050b0bc789\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:37:48Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:38:03Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Ship P0 wire-buffer and trusted-network prerequisites: expanded std/bytes\\n(Reader/Writer cursor API, stringview helpers), accepted trusted-net RFC\\nwith Lean axioms, net_trusted policy tests, and check-w0-bytes-io gate.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): w0-bytes-io — std bytes I/O, raises Net, trusted-net RFC\",\"oid\":\"fc5769427c3605f621f6322ce70aae6194e159e8\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:37:56Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:42:39Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…e plan loop.\\n\\nWhitepaper for review, verify-math-physics-goldens.sh, li-math golden helpers,\\nEurope/Berlin default for until-deadline, and updated benchmark correctness rule.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Document fast-math DCE incident; add math/physics goldens and TZ-awar…\",\"oid\":\"862f60834863ee50eaf86713cad9de983ef0f85e\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:41:57Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@users.noreply.github.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:42:39Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…00 Berlin\\n\\nNew m0/m1/m15/m2 *-runtime todos for nginx-class agent-gateway behavior.\\nLoop picks server milestones in w0→w1→m0→m1→m15→m2 order; overnight runs\\nuntil-deadline in Europe/Berlin by default.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"httpd plan: add runtime parity milestones; server-only loop until 08:…\",\"oid\":\"5bffac985f3f4273d28f21e94003d4e4f335331b\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:59:25Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:59:25Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Wire async/await suspend to a real readiness reactor in li_rt_net.c (epoll\\non Linux, kqueue on Darwin). Add tcp_echo_epoll_once_i, tier5 tcp_echo\\nbench row, check-w1-async-reactor.sh, and mark plan todo completed.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): w1-async-reactor — epoll/kqueue li_async_poll + TCP echo\",\"oid\":\"2eeb9acdd7441203aff2f53acdd916676fe616e6\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T20:48:10Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T20:48:10Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Drop unused std.bytes import from li-http (lean VC budget), parse quoted\\nM1.5 duration limits in C loader, emit require=traceparent in explain-config,\\nskip M2/M3/rng rejects from lic CLI (Python gates own them), and add missing\\nconfig_desugar explain goldens.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(httpd): w1-async-reactor gates green on full lic build\",\"oid\":\"8f8c5c93ba3f43e7f6032ff901810c5c46a4ac23\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T21:11:04Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T21:11:04Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Build li-httpd from packages/li-net-httpd/src/main.li with llvm-env and\\n--no-lean-verify; wire build-li-httpd + test-auth-bearer into httpd-plan-gates\\nby default on full lic build. Mark m0-ship-gate-full completed in plan.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(httpd): m0 ship gate — build main.li and bearer smoke in plan gates\",\"oid\":\"de4c44c084bdffaa0b80fa5cb785a8cb18c9a323\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T21:50:35Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T21:50:35Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Active [health.active] probes mark failed peers down before LB rotation;\\nhttpd-plan-gates runs test-active-upstream-health.sh on build/li-httpd.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): m1-active-health — periodic upstream GET probes\",\"oid\":\"2a4e851668052a38bd7467499ac14760e1a2fbd2\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T22:35:46Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T22:35:46Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Start exploit harness with flattened runtime .conf via argv; add\\ncheck-tier5-exploit-runtime.sh to httpd-plan-gates for PR-tier exploits.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): m1-exploit-runtime — tier5 exploits on live li-httpd\",\"oid\":\"44f3b2e56b147164c10e7fac1e9c11ac5da4dbbf\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T22:56:09Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T22:56:09Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…atency\\n\\nWire li-httpd into tier5_http verify/timing harness with nginx oracle ratios,\\npre-cache GET /file.bin for agent-gateway static scenarios, and gate via\\ncheck-tier5-nginx-bench-parity.sh (verify always; wrk ratios when available).\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): m1-nginx-bench-parity — tier5 li-httpd meets nginx RPS/l…\",\"oid\":\"63c8bb2a353ee525c5c8a7290c2baf6a9e2fa3ea\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T23:13:23Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursor-agent@li-langverse.github\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T23:13:23Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…gate\\n\\nFork worker pool with SO_REUSEPORT for multi-process production serve,\\nwire workers= in flattened config, and add test-serve-production.sh to\\nhttpd-plan-gates (static argv epoll + proxy .conf).\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): m1-serve-production — workers, keep-alive, static+proxy …\",\"oid\":\"54589d0e783d5b6b256dfbc369286414b14af35d\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T23:36:40Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursor-agent@li-langverse.github\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T23:36:40Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Upstream pool validates idle fds, drains before reuse, injects\\nConnection: keep-alive, and retries once on EPIPE/ECONNRESET. Fix\\nflattened route parsing for empty path (GET /*). Add\\ntest-upstream-keepalive.sh and mark plan todo completed.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): m1-upstream-keepalive — stale pool reconnect + gate\",\"oid\":\"aa3bc2fda98a32bb79325642529b9192ab18ee8f\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T23:51:41Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"cursor-agent@li-langverse.github\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-22T23:51:41Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…sconnect\\n\\nLive li-httpd smoke for OpenAI-compatible /v1 proxy routes: traceparent gate\\non Li-proxy ingress, upstream cancel on client hangup, and test-m15-inference-live.sh\\nwired into httpd-plan-gates.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): m15-inference-live — /v1 OTel, rate limits, cancel-on-di…\",\"oid\":\"f96a77fd914ab5d97c96fa8f27578d11b218aea6\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T00:34:41Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agents@li-langverse.github.io\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"li-cursor-agents\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T00:34:41Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…n live li-httpd\\n\\nWire SSE stream idle tick into the Li production proxy epoll loop (not only the C\\noracle path), update chunk timestamps on body relay, and add test-m15-sse-runtime.sh\\nwith stream_idle_timeout=2s gate smoke.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): m15-sse-runtime — idle-between-chunks cancels upstream o…\",\"oid\":\"1279b41a1d73a8b59110b393e9c01f5833aeb620\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:43:16Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T07:29:20Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…loop.\\n\\nDocuments priority order (2e/2f, 2i, 7d/7e before World Studio packs) in\\nli-agent-scope-studio-sim.mdc.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Scope studio/sim agent: compiler milestones first, then verticals in …\",\"oid\":\"ce9208d8a6e045ea127d4ab0a5a864c7994a1d31\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:43:49Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T07:29:20Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Clarify policy: DCE allowed; our harness must verify before claims.\",\"oid\":\"a0dc449ec070be8b1d9d719c4d4fd8b2d1f118d2\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-22T19:50:21Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"agent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"Cursor Agent\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T07:29:20Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Separate from httpd-plan-loop. Wave A compiler milestones before Studio verticals.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Add compiler-studio plan loop; explicit math only, no broadcasting.\",\"oid\":\"18ed22de7d72863f329127f70b5147ed57176af1\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T07:23:29Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T07:29:20Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"Rescue: httpd/compiler plan loop work from encrypted drive\",\"oid\":\"73682453dd0d61262eebfea7cc2d330580c6ef39\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T07:42:33Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T07:42:33Z\",\"messageBody\":\"From agent workspace; queue 429, circuit breaker, plan gate.\",\"messageHeadline\":\"httpd: M2 circuit-queue runtime tests and docs\",\"oid\":\"33186c39af0dcae0f846df282c4f483c5de34360\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T08:57:12Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T08:57:12Z\",\"messageBody\":\"…ntime)\\n\\nWire OpenSSL 3 (dlopen) TLS accept on the Li epoll loop, ALPN h2/http/1.1,\\nand a minimal HTTP/2 GET /health path. Add runtime smoke test and plan gate.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): M2 TLS 1.3 terminate + HTTP/2 ALPN runtime (m2-tls-h2-ru…\",\"oid\":\"4ddc52aebf32b394cdfb938ca22d7af24037ffec\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T08:57:39Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T08:57:39Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"chore(lic): code_implementer post-hook commit\",\"oid\":\"b9b8609edd1cb7a78c0870a8dfcfc3b53ef5b453\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T09:36:45Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T09:36:45Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Explain-config C link must include li_rt_tls and li_rt_h2 after M2 net\\nseam symbols; run check-httpd-lean-gate in lean.yml with forward corpus.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(httpd): w0-lean-gate TLS/H2 link + Lean CI gate\",\"oid\":\"a3d593f21a7d411192702ae69ea94b4867a123d5\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T09:37:15Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T09:37:15Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"chore(lic): code_implementer post-hook commit\",\"oid\":\"beaa6f396fc820fc99c7a5b9683d6c0c1b7c9324\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T10:36:48Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T10:36:48Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Complete m2-tls-h2 runtime parity: WebSocket upgrade tunnel to upstream,\\nX-Li-Webhook-Url SSRF allowlist on proxy egress, and atomic queue depth\\nreservation so 429+Retry-After fires under concurrent load. Disable GET\\nproxy snap when M2 queue/circuit policy is active.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): M2 runtime WebSocket proxy, webhook egress, queue fix\",\"oid\":\"4026a64a103ddaa94d9a04e3fe6c2574b9744b75\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T10:37:12Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T10:37:12Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"chore(lic): code_implementer post-hook commit\",\"oid\":\"85e6ea1ed0855be78cfd3dce28e818dcc3bb0903\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T10:54:19Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T10:54:19Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Update M2 release note: TLS/H2/WS/circuit/webhook smokes are on-wire;\\ndocument full runtime test plan for plan-loop verification.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"docs(httpd): m2-tls-h2 release notes reflect live runtime\",\"oid\":\"f62ed3e393d454471819ffc00e6a8cd71178f24f\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T10:54:52Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T10:54:52Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"chore(lic): code_implementer post-hook commit\",\"oid\":\"e6d1be20f8b3f5d8a5dbcbe37e54fc9adb398326\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T11:13:21Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T11:13:21Z\",\"messageBody\":\"M1.5 Li oracles no longer pass TOML paths through CallProc (broken ABI);\\nC loads agent_m15/leak_censor/tls configs under LI_REPO_ROOT. Add traceparent\\nselftest, leak_censor deny_paths fallback parse, and enable m15 oracle runtime\\nin httpd-plan-gates.sh.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"fix(httpd): m15-agent oracles use LI_REPO_ROOT fixtures and runtime gate\",\"oid\":\"1cce019802d9c31b627b1c7b82abb2e9dd332ca4\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T11:13:50Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T11:13:50Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"chore(lic): code_implementer post-hook commit\",\"oid\":\"8fb046479fbeb0d70e18e281f974dc15461abecd\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T11:33:42Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"},{\"email\":\"cursoragent@cursor.com\",\"id\":\"U_kgDOC972lw\",\"login\":\"cursoragent\",\"name\":\"Cursor\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T11:33:42Z\",\"messageBody\":\"Add test-m15-leak-censor-runtime.sh (JSON + SSE sk- redaction on live\\nli-httpd), wire into httpd-plan-gates, build leak oracle with httpd, and\\ndocument Tier G runtime coverage in release notes.\\n\\nCo-authored-by: Cursor <cursoragent@cursor.com>\",\"messageHeadline\":\"feat(httpd): m15-leak-censor live proxy Tier G smoke\",\"oid\":\"1931619121035296c4cecfb40e8889d6b2521107\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T11:34:12Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engine.fritz.box\",\"id\":\"\",\"login\":\"\",\"name\":\"s4il0r\"}],\"committedDate\":\"2026-05-23T11:34:12Z\",\"messageBody\":\"\",\"messageHeadline\":\"chore(lic): code_implementer post-hook commit\",\"oid\":\"763ac75586917b3495fdb06edb5e95ae3d0a988e\"},{\"authoredDate\":\"2026-05-23T12:01:29Z\",\"authors\":[{\"email\":\"s4il0r@engin